## üìà Version History

### v1.4.0 - August 19, 2025
**Status:** ‚úÖ **STABLE**  
**Type:** Minor Release  
**Compatibility:** Backward compatible with v1.3.x  

#### Major Features
- **Network Spoofing Service**: IP/MAC address spoofing, browser fingerprint modification
- **Advanced Rate Limiting**: Provider-specific intelligent rate limiting
- **Enhanced Anti-Detection**: Request interception, tracking script blocking
- **Production Infrastructure**: Docker deployment with PostgreSQL and Redis

#### Performance Improvements
- DuckDuckGo success rate: 30% ‚Üí 85%
- Response time: 6-12 seconds (includes anti-detection delays)
- Memory impact: +2-3MB for spoofing services

#### New Environment Variables
- `ENABLE_NETWORK_SPOOFING`
- `ENABLE_IP_SPOOFING`
- `ENABLE_MAC_ADDRESS_SPOOFING`
- `ENABLE_FINGERPRINT_SPOOFING`
- `REQUEST_DELAY_MIN` / `REQUEST_DELAY_MAX`

### v1.3.0 - 2025-01-XX
**Status:** ‚úÖ **STABLE**  
**Type:** Minor Release  
**Compatibility:** Backward compatible with v1.2.x  

#### Major Features
- **Chamber of Commerce Processing (COCP)**: Automatic chamberofcommerce.com URL processing
- **Yelp RESTful Scraping**: Enhanced Yelp integration with deep website analysis
- **Directory URL Fix**: Eliminated directory URL warnings
- **Enhanced Deep Scraping**: Up to 20 pages per business website

#### Bug Fixes
- Domain blacklist persistence between sessions
- Rate limiting improvements for 429 errors
- Demo mode references cleanup

### v1.2.0 - 2024-XX-XX
**Status:** ‚úÖ **STABLE**  
**Type:** Minor Release  
**Compatibility:** Backward compatible with v1.1.x  

#### Major Features
- **Per-Industry Domain Blacklists**: Industry-specific domain filtering
- **Enhanced Wildcard Support**: Advanced pattern matching (`*.domain.com`, `domain.*`)
- **Theme-Aware Interface**: Automatic light/dark mode adaptation
- **Next.js Image Optimization**: WebP/AVIF conversion, responsive delivery

#### Performance Improvements
- 25-50% smaller image file sizes
- Improved Core Web Vitals scores
- Enhanced SEO performance

### v1.1.0 - 2024-XX-XX
**Status:** ‚úÖ **STABLE**  
**Type:** Minor Release  
**Compatibility:** Backward compatible with v1.0.x  

#### Major Features
- **Smart Industry Expansion**: Automatic industry category expansion
- **Advanced BBB Business Discovery**: Real-time BBB website scraping
- **Precise ZIP Radius Validation**: Geolocation-based distance calculation
- **Enhanced Search Engine Architecture**: Multi-strategy search implementation

#### Technical Improvements
- Puppeteer-based BBB scraping
- Anti-bot countermeasures
- Haversine formula for distance calculation
- Comprehensive error handling

### v1.0.0 - 2024-01-XX
**Status:** ‚úÖ **STABLE**  
**Type:** Major Release  
**Compatibility:** Initial stable release  

#### Core Features
- **Complete Scraping Engine**: Puppeteer-based web scraping
- **Multi-Provider Search**: DuckDuckGo, Bing, Yandex integration
- **Industry Management**: Predefined and custom industry categories
- **Location-Based Search**: ZIP code-centered search with radius
- **Data Management**: IndexedDB storage with CRUD operations
- **Export Capabilities**: CSV, XLSX, XLS, ODS, PDF, JSON formats
- **Responsive UI**: Mobile-friendly design with dark mode

#### Technical Stack
- **Frontend:** Next.js 14, React 18, TypeScript
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS
- **Storage:** IndexedDB
- **Testing:** Jest, React Testing Library
- **Build:** Next.js optimized production builds

